---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started | StartMicrolearning" description="Begin your microlearning journey with fundamental concepts, business case development, and organizational readiness assessment.">
  <div class="getting-started-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Getting Started</h1>
      <p class="page-description">
        Build a solid foundation for microlearning success in your organization
      </p>
      <hr class="page-rule" />
    </header>

    <div class="content-sections">
      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>What is Microlearning?</h2>
        <p>
          Microlearning is a targeted educational approach that delivers content in small, 
          focused chunks. Each learning unit is designed to achieve a specific learning 
          objective and can be consumed in 2-10 minutes.
        </p>
        
        <div class="key-characteristics">
          <h3>Key Characteristics</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Bite-sized content:</strong> Short, focused learning modules</li>
            <li><strong>Just-in-time delivery:</strong> Available when and where needed</li>
            <li><strong>Mobile-friendly:</strong> Optimized for various devices</li>
            <li><strong>Performance-focused:</strong> Directly applicable to work tasks</li>
            <li><strong>Engaging format:</strong> Interactive and multimedia-rich</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Business Case for Microlearning</h2>
        <p>
          Understanding the business value of microlearning is crucial for gaining 
          organizational support and securing resources for your initiatives.
        </p>
        
        <div class="business-benefits">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h4>Increased Engagement</h4>
            <p>Short, focused content maintains learner attention and reduces cognitive overload.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h4>Better Retention</h4>
            <p>Spaced repetition and focused content improve long-term knowledge retention.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h4>Cost Effective</h4>
            <p>Lower development costs and reduced time away from work for training.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <h4>Flexible Delivery</h4>
            <p>Learn anytime, anywhere, on any device - fitting into busy work schedules.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Organizational Readiness</h2>
        <p>
          Assess your organization's readiness for microlearning implementation 
          with these key considerations:
        </p>
        
        <div class="readiness-checklist">
          <div class="checklist-item">
            <h4>Technology Infrastructure</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Learning Management System (LMS) capabilities</li>
              <li>Mobile device policies and access</li>
              <li>Bandwidth and connectivity</li>
              <li>Content authoring tools</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="checklist-item">
            <h4>Organizational Culture</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Leadership support for learning initiatives</li>
              <li>Employee openness to new learning formats</li>
              <li>Time allocation for learning activities</li>
              <li>Performance measurement alignment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="checklist-item">
            <h4>Content Strategy</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Existing training content audit</li>
              <li>Subject matter expert availability</li>
              <li>Content maintenance processes</li>
              <li>Quality assurance procedures</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Common Misconceptions</h2>
        <p>
          Avoid these common pitfalls when planning your microlearning strategy:
        </p>
        
        <div class="misconceptions">
          <div class="misconception">
            <h4>❌ "Just Make Everything Shorter"</h4>
            <p>Microlearning isn't about reducing content length - it's about focused, purposeful design.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="misconception">
            <h4>❌ "One Size Fits All"</h4>
            <p>Different topics and audiences require different microlearning approaches and formats.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="misconception">
            <h4>❌ "Technology First"</h4>
            <p>Start with learning objectives and audience needs, then select appropriate technology.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="misconception">
            <h4>❌ "Set and Forget"</h4>
            <p>Effective microlearning requires ongoing maintenance, updates, and performance monitoring.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Next Steps</h2>
        <p>
          Ready to move forward? Here's your recommended learning path:
        </p>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
          <div class="step-card">
            <h4>1. Learn the MICRO Framework</h4>
            <p>Master our systematic approach to microlearning design</p>
            <a href="/design-framework" class="step-link">Explore Framework →</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step-card">
            <h4>2. Assess Your Content</h4>
            <p>Evaluate existing training materials for microlearning potential</p>
            <a href="/design-framework#content-strategy" class="step-link">Content Strategy →</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step-card">
            <h4>3. Plan Your Pilot</h4>
            <p>Start small with a focused pilot project to demonstrate value</p>
            <a href="/implementation" class="step-link">Implementation Guide →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .getting-started-page {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-primary);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .page-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .page-rule {
    height: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border: none;
    width: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .content-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4) 0 calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .content-section h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 1.5);
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .business-benefits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .benefit-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .benefit-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .readiness-checklist {
    display: grid;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .checklist-item {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .checklist-item h4 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .checklist-item ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .checklist-item li {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .misconceptions {
    display: grid;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .misconception {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .misconception h4 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .misconception p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .next-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .step-card {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .step-card h4 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .step-card p {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .step-link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .step-link:hover,
  .step-link:focus {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .business-benefits,
    .next-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>